      <Placemark>
        <name>Endless Summer Watersport</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ADbDBKtTqleiBnopiC9tc2QfA4DZ0oQrl9d6Fjqw1ayKH2VvBKMD_HJ71VnyahzqLPdgOkbZbftoCC3s7z1md8T1RY3AgOcV4goOxHr3_2seCpKkQhvckkohpLPj-bp3LYMHPfCbCdLHLt0nfrErErm3znG9CIJ-aR-4SO7iBqDqNF5LmM0dfPhv4QvBKO1wk4Q-P6xyrdk9iLqfAOUrubkEFaRHkn27I_s5DmQUh5KZ5ij4vuKtSX9q97vsEfSAkQ?authuser=3&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>𝗩𝗶𝗱𝗲𝗼 𝗱𝗲𝗹 𝗟𝘂𝗴𝗮𝗿: N/A.<br><br>𝗜𝗡𝗙𝗢𝗥𝗠𝗔𝗖𝗜𝗢𝗡:<br>𝗧𝗲𝗹𝗲𝗳𝗼𝗻𝗼: 939-283-8189<br>𝗛𝗼𝗿𝗮𝗿𝗶𝗼𝘀: Lunes a Domingo - 9pm a 5pm<br>𝗪𝗲𝗯: N/A<br><br>𝗖𝗢𝗡𝗖𝗘𝗣𝗧𝗢: Endless Summer Watersport ofrece experiencias acuáticas como alquiler de jet skis, banana boat, kayaks, paddle boards, botes de pedales y renta de sillas y sombrillas. Ideal para familias y grupos que buscan diversión en el agua. Con el cupón de Roadtripeado podras disfrutar de un descuento de 15% en cualquier servicio.<br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ADbDBKvPOi-ZWCTTbUuS7SekEuu6TqlXL8K6-YLes7Ew3ayCDymRTJVyjIKnj_PxP63VRjiR4UjvrCgWMGefJci3gKM3T3Oxge-tlX5qYgGIooSXPU2_D9kwJdbKubh0f0c2aS8XetWbaK3exmyaM5XCzxbI71R6FxHOCVEPu7x9CI1ibRFi65gKXCuH3TJT_eyMhQNEqvp7zWNNJoYcgwlk50PUzmmWHChgiiQ4Sa5okirSp5VNZgkEWQJaFjNtAA?authuser=3&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ADbDBKsV4PHwoNyQuLX3rejqKMVM5AVYqvWO4dydVZ9TR_jUwC6xPQZi7OB6_BFctwzm-R2yV0nt42rGRBVaSjZqJcuMD_IUK8yPprvGTP1I7wZyP90dfAHwT1TljWDnSyFsUNwNjvTch0VmtSv4oXgq2L0p4w5Bl4Esm4b38P9brJM8j4zT6_6tLPGiQd3qyQ2hqpitvD_tmZKJXgD94HLwUHDHqKgvTJEBsJKNj-u0cOVe2fzHjsFhQa_D0jmfeQ?authuser=3&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" />]]></description>
