      <Placemark>
        <name>Camp Liara</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ADbDBKtD5Fn-DE7G0XsjXt2LrdDEduAA7_xa8nLs_AgMvoUdQ8eBvP1Ge0ZO_3uVYEHjZz_SB-olxGoCSO8SeKBAFThRBqdPj48YzGq1hd9G-9ubFO4Z-LZpUoebYG_GSUETn5OZf4kW-Nns7_LWrCwn46p5nwJgvtBAv89C1PtHyV_k43Idw2_PwbHwjWthWhCMFY0g29bdMnUjn38tHjg4htbmriJsLfAL4JcvKrQuNN05nsvq1ogjFlVS8SL7VA?authuser=3&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>𝗩𝗶𝗱𝗲𝗼 𝗱𝗲𝗹 𝗟𝘂𝗴𝗮𝗿: N/A<br><br>𝗥𝗲𝘀𝗲𝗿𝘃𝗮 𝗔𝗾𝘂𝗶: https://www.airbnb.mx/rooms/1200233796449452464?guests=1&adults=1&s=67&unique_share_id=3df5837a-1121-4c60-bcb9-fdfff7a686f1<br><br>𝗗𝗲𝘁𝗮𝗹𝗹𝗲𝘀: Camp Liara, el mejor camper de Isabela. Es un alojamiento para 2 personas. Ubicado a minutos de hermosas playas, deliciosos restaurantes y del mejor entretenimiento que el área noroeste ofrece.<br>¡Disfruta de la experiencia de Camp Liara!<br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ADbDBKu8gQerIenOgi3oJenLIEVXDKB9zSzAuvucfdjSsTTxuEwPVbdqC9zPSHw7TPQ4WIVV5W0PeNm4mHcNP7y0ANkxil-ARY9ZEZWWZ6TqIg7EQOLiUYWI4VECX7dbxxgjGi1I3w80GM6cW0pPRtlidwXZ8DTYVFzdI5WpaoB4-OoefuYiuPau4aJTlSFwnI-D8xWY8QPDm-dVYphze42Ts7H0LSnXtda0r_rqj7zIuqaw7yKlf4csD3UWlM92-A?authuser=3&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ADbDBKvYr7rM7MgTTVfr_2lKRl1GNqflLbwKLJuum8Wn513VkWUj7Ynhvco0MlbXtXxJAsQ6GYsBUumWh6yDOFANBq4aFrzv7_C_VsWQwphurGWjgL45D3yNv1whizhzM6DAfwcUUlo9Ib2_EAqdnzc98V4NOk9p4qYt9twLqnIgoC0ucus4DGLfdjJ5EjFy1PdSEZAFVX4qamg4QEEPJbAmHgqA_I7HVHlSrLSnU0iBOfEkWlmAQ0iw5z_uXctzCg?authuser=3&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ADbDBKt6nsa2EfoHZlIrZGXmDbo7zLPTMspHHevvpt-3GaEdGJlsJXvwtk97srj4K4WZkRj8Tncj3lcbdNoHIzkS4C3HKXIB1bTUMKh962PCEpODSO38kFJzJlCMjehtzAeq-OShQUIA3iGx0UFiTbSOhMFpdFtJNoAR8V4AD-fVExLNQ4ZzAJi1-sFqP_sEJ9zVJUI0ZV9_T-LQ6eLeSJDRv1tKijbW7Odw74gaUROipOWnDnr3daioe-4Qmmz8Ow?authuser=3&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img